scenario: Liam wants to purchase affordable cards and learn more about the game to improve his skills.

Logical Flow
Homepage
Liam accesses the homepage, which features a simple design with popular cards and links to all the event that related to it.
Exploring Educational Content
He navigates to the "Event" section filled with engaging tutorials and videos or he can go to store and attend the tutorial.
Browsing Affordable Cards
Liam uses filters to find cards within his budget.
Adding Items to Wishlist
He adds desired cards to his wishlist to review with his parents later.
Completing Purchase
Liam proceeds to checkout.
Order Confirmation
He receives a confirmation and eagerly awaits the delivery.
UI Considerations
Simplified Navigation: Easy-to-find sections like "Learn to Play" and "Affordable Cards."
